itunes:summary:
Ross Patterson and Dan Hollaway discuss Trump beating the coronavirus and how it will affect the election and the upcoming debate, how New York and Los Angeles might shut down again, what will happen to the governors of the states that enforced prolonged shutdowns, and why the NBA is seeing record lows for the NBA Finals games between the Lakers and the Heat.
